        "id": "prob_001",
        "timestamp": "2024-10-27T16:08:32Z",
        "problem": "Webhook signature verification failing with 400 error",
        "solution": "Body-parser was consuming the request body before signature verification. Added raw body middleware that stores original buffer at req.rawBody. Changed webhook handler to use req.rawBody for stripe.webhooks.constructEvent().",
